2009931489.text: "The repression of eIF2alpha phosphorylation by exendin-4 and forskolin may restore Bcl-2 expression and thus prevent cytochrome C release and caspase 3 activation by salubrinal and CPA, but they have little effect on palmitate induced apoptosis."
